songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Oh, Nadine
I woke up from a dream last night
Where all the skies were green
You were the Sun
Down on the wave came your daylight
Oh, Nadine, you were the Sun

[Verse 2]
Oh, Nadine, oh
Oh, Nadine
Down on the wave came your daylight
Hmm, hmm, hmm
Hmm, hmm, hmm

[Verse 3]
You were in my dream, oh
Oh, Nadine
Down on the wave came your daylight
Oh, Nadine
I have a funny feeling you'd be so good to me

[Verse 4]
Oh, Nadine
You told me
You woke up from the dream

[Verse 5]
Oh, you were in my dream
Oh, oh, oh
songs.title: Oh Nadine
